      "body" : "I find that reading the large database files just before running bitcoind makes the total start up time much lower.  Probably because I have enough RAM to cache the whole files in RAM, and reading them sequentially is faster than the random order that bitcoin reads them while it's starting:\r\n\r\nmd5sum ~/.bitcoin/{addr,blk}*.dat; bitcoind -daemon\r\n",
